## Dataset Notice

NucleiMapper uses the RV-PBS
(Ramakrishna Vivekananda Peripheral Blood Smear)
dataset for training.

The RV-PBS dataset is NOT included or redistributed
within this repository.

Users must obtain the dataset from its original source
and comply with its respective license and terms of use.

The provided `crop_dataset.py` utility reads the original
CVAT annotations and generates classification-ready
white blood cell crops while preserving the natural
peripheral blood smear background.

Natural smear backgrounds are intentionally preserved
because they better represent real-world microscopy
images than artificially alpha-masked or black-background
cutouts.

No ownership is claimed over the RV-PBS dataset.

